value: Marital status and fertility of the population aged 15 and over by county and settlement type of Hungary from 2011 to 2022.

To download data:
Click on the url -> Dimensions drag them to columns,rows or sections", -> In columns drag "Census year" ,"sex", "Legal marital status", "Types of settlement" and In rows drag  " county, region" and  "Age group "  -> accordingly it creates table  -> click download.
